thread.title: Mr LEAHY

author: Mr LEAHY
title: Mr LEAHY
text: I ordered my part and was it would be delivered on the 31st of Jan. When it didn't arrive I was told it was on the way from France. Two days later there was still no sign and the tracking ID just said it was dispatched so I rang again and was told it was on the way from Belgium now?? Another two days later the part arrived. I was told I would be contacted by customer care to discuss getting something back on my account but heard nothing back as of yet.
